cc:Work.dc:title: Jack-O-Lantern Carving
cc:Work.dc:description: I Think this is meant to look cute, but this little kid creeps me out. It's so creepy! It's like he is jabbing the knife deep into the poor eye of the sleeping jack-o-lantern, gaaaah! It's also odd how much the jack o lantern resembles the face of the boy.
